Please stay by my side forever!

276
00:29:43,220 --> 00:29:48,090
♫ Under the waning moon ♫

277
00:29:48,090 --> 00:29:51,720
♫ Dense fog wanders ♫

278
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:57,650
♫ Gradually, the maze-like night ♫

279
00:29:57,650 --> 00:30:01,860
♫ Is dawning ♫

